name: SHOOT THAT POISON ARROW
description: The fourth and final Anatomical Pin-Up which is a spin on the classic pin-up girl. The poses, facial expressions and attire (or lack of) is reminiscent of the 1950's pin-up girls. The difference, is the gross anatomy. The point of removing the skin of certain body parts is to humanize and de-sexualize the female form. To see what lies underneath is not that different from the male form. Do you think she's sexy now? 4200px X 6600px by @dehisenceart 2021
